commit.message: Cleanup whitespace

Use svg--plist-delete instead of org-plist-delete

The former is actually a copy of the latter, and because it is defined
in the `svg' library, it is actually available here, because we already
require that library.

Fix bug reading stroke width from existing face

When svg-lib-style-from-face runs on a face with a box line-width, the resulting stroke is "stroke" instead of the number
